    ],
    "image_count": 3,
    "description": "Remember when the White House ballroom was going to cost taxpayers nothing? Not a dime. Not a penny. Not even the loose change rattling around in the federal couch cushions.\n\nIt was, we were told, a gift. A patriotic offering from generous private donors. A monument to American greatness, underwritten entirely by someone else. Fast forward a bit, and that \u201cfree\u201d ballroom now comes with a $1 billion price tag for taxpayers. Funny how that works.",
    "title": "The Ballroom"
  },
